WEBVTT

00:00:27.631 --> 00:00:31.611
trước họng súng đầy,
tôi viết nó lên bảng,

00:00:31.611 --> 00:00:35.041
tạm dừng để chúng
chỉ ra từ trái nghĩa

00:00:35.041 --> 00:00:37.525
Của tôi - của bạn

00:00:37.525 --> 00:00:40.045
Đời sống - cái chết

00:00:40.045 --> 00:00:43.945
Đã đứng? Sẽ ngồi

00:00:43.945 --> 00:00:45.945
Một - nhiều

00:00:45.945 --> 00:00:48.155
Đầy - Trống

00:00:48.155 --> 00:00:50.615
Khẩu súng?

00:00:50.615 --> 00:00:52.535
Khẩu súng.

00:00:52.535 --> 00:00:55.309
Trong khoảnh khắc,
nhanh như khoảng cách giữa

00:00:55.309 --> 00:00:59.399
ánh sáng và âm thanh,
bọn trẻ chỉ nhìn tôi,

00:00:59.399 --> 00:01:03.879
và sau đó là trận bão
câu trả lời --